hildanalodge.com +254 (0) 792 690 931", "text": "Reservation Contact stay@thehildanalodge.com +254 (0) 792 690 931"}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/9", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 780.3759179261618, "r": 163.81328274229625, "b": 770.9284851820785, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 21]}], "orig": "Terms and Conditions:", "text": "Terms and Conditions:", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/10", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/0"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 765.320906053079, "r": 509.466025080848, "b": 755.9471662321164, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 99]}], "orig": "1. Bookings are accepted on the condition that guests have their own comprehensive travel insurance", "text": "Bookings are accepted on the condition that guests have their own comprehensive travel insurance", "enumerated": true, "marker": "1."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/11", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 750.320906678079, "r": 335.87524970307226, "b": 725.9471674821165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 68]}], "orig": "cover. 2. Room check-out time is 10:00 a.m. on the day of departure.", "text": "cover. 2. Room check-out time is 10:00 a.m. on the day of departure."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/12", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/1"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 720.320907928079, "r": 523.1962625161049, "b": 680.9471693571164, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 293]}], "orig": "3. Late Departures: for guests departing in the afternoon, room check out is still 10:00 a.m., and a surcharge of Ksh3,500 applies for meals and activities until afternoon departure. Late departures MUST be pre-booked and are subject to the availability of vehicles/services to cater for this.", "text": "Late Departures: for guests departing in the afternoon, room check out is still 10:00 a.m., and a surcharge of Ksh3,500 applies for meals and activities until afternoon departure. Late departures MUST be pre-booked and are subject to the availability of vehicles/services to cater for this.", "enumerated": true, "marker": "3."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/13", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/1"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 675.3209098030791, "r": 502.3195376420683, "b": 650.9471706071165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 159]}], "orig": "4. We reserve the right to review published rates in the event of currency exchange rate fluctuation, increases in costs or taxes, that are beyond our control.", "text": "We reserve the right to review published rates in the event of currency exchange rate fluctuation, increases in costs or taxes, that are beyond our control.", "enumerated": true, "marker": "4."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/14", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/1"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 645.320911053079, "r": 227.36000654954108, "b": 635.9471712321165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 39]}], "orig": "5. Children under 4 years old are free.", "text": "Children under 4 years old are free.", "enumerated": true, "marker": "5."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/15", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 615.320912303079, "r": 143.94234221715215, "b": 605.9471724821165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 13]}], "orig": "BOOKING TERMS", "text": "BOOKING TERMS", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/16", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 600.320912928079, "r": 533.5608272268981, "b": 545.9471749821164, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 330]}], "orig": "All provisional bookings are given an automatic expiry date (normally 2 weeks from the date the provisional booking is made). You are required to confirm the booking prior to the expiry date to avoid the automatic release of the booking. If you require more time to confirm the booking, the expiry date may be extended on request.", "text": "All provisional bookings are given an automatic expiry date (normally 2 weeks from the date the provisional booking is made). You are required to confirm the booking prior to the expiry date to avoid the automatic release of the booking. If you require more time to confirm the booking, the expiry date may be extended on request."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/17", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 525.3209160530791, "r": 530.2748009175657, "b": 455.94717873211647, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 489]}], "orig": "Bookings are confirmed upon receipt of a 20% deposit of the total reservation cost. The balance is payable in full 30 days prior to arrival (or if the booking is within 45 days, immediately upon booking).If final payment is not received, then the Company is entitled to release the rooms and any other services with no further liability. In such circumstances, the deposit will not be refunded, and any reimbursement of payment received will be dealt with per the cancellation terms below:", "text": "Bookings are confirmed upon receipt of a 20% deposit of the total reservation cost. The balance is payable in full 30 days prior to arrival (or if the booking is within 45 days, immediately upon booking).If final payment is not received, then the Company is entitled to release the rooms and any other services with no further liability. In such circumstances, the deposit will not be refunded, and any reimbursement of payment received will be dealt with per the cancellation terms below:"}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/18", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 420.3209204280791, "r": 512.5427602188008, "b": 365.9471824821165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 141]}], "orig": "CANCELLATION TERMS 45 days and 30 days prior to arrival: 30% of the full booking value is forfeited, the balance will be net of bank charges.", "text": "CANCELLATION TERMS 45 days and 30 days prior to arrival: 30% of the full booking value is forfeited, the balance will be net of bank charges."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/19", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 360.3209229280791, "r": 461.4174344971477, "b": 350.9471831071165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 93]}], "orig": "Less than 30 days prior to arrival and no-shows: 100% of the full booking value is forfeited.", "text": "Less than 30 days prior to arrival and no-shows: 100% of the full booking value is forfeited."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/20", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 59.5275551196851, "t": 330.3209241780791, "r": 434.14579913346597, "b": 320.9471843571165, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 87]}], "orig": "*No refund will be given for clients who join a safari but leave before its completion.", "text": "*No refund will be given for clients who join a safari but leave before its completion."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/21", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, 